   <abstract>Gift of Ann Brown Wright, photo taken in Neopolis in 1940. "Uncle" Sam Bond was born around 1849 at the Cheairs "Quarter." He was the overseer after the civil war.  Pictured L to R, Bob Lowery, Sarah Lou Brown, Sarah Francis Quick, "Uncle" Sam Bond, Dora Ann Brown, H. Hugh Brown, Lovenia Davis, Marjorie Lowery.</abstract>
